Distribution . Cosmopolitan. In the eastern Pacific it has been recorded off the west coast of the Baja California Peninsula ( Lavaniegos & Hereu 2009 ; Lavaniegos 2014 , 2017 ), in the Gulf of California, off Jalisco and Colima , western Mexico , and off Ecuador ( Brusca & Hendrickx 2005 ; García-Madrigal 2007 ;
Gasca et al . 2012
).
